r years ago.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6556913029791985e-27, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement,Dujardin claimed she made an 'error of judgement'and is 'deeply ashamed' of her actions.\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The scandal has once again raised theissue of the treatment of horses in sports.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tbrowser thatsupports HTML5 \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tvideo  Up Next  The Netherlands have found themselves under the spotlight afterconvicted rapist Steven van de Velde\\u00a0was selected for their volleyball team.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1200, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0690284963693843e-15, \"text\": \"JavaScript\", \"types\": [\"Q9143\", \"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\"}, {\"begin\": 1272, \"end\": 1277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.511675187219524e-13, \"text\": \"HTML5\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\"}, {\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999853032361403, \"rank\": 1.4695809965954745e-05, \"text\": \"The Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Net